 "body": "<p>The guidance in these pages relates to solicitors practising as self-employed individuals or as partners in a partnership or limited liability partnership. It does not cover companies authorised to provide legal services under the Solicitors Regulation Authority rules or solicitors working as employees.</p>\n",
